blish again\n1160: - [ ] Verify existing Deployment is updated\n1161: - [ ] Verify existing Service is updated\n1162: - [ ] Verify no duplicate resources are created\n1163: \n1164: **Verification**: Publish same agent twice and verify update behavior\n1165: \n1166: ---\n1167: \n1168: ### Task 81: Test session timeout configuration\n1169: - [ ] Verify default sessionTimeout is \"15m\"\n1170: - [ ] Verify default maxSessionDuration is \"8h\"\n1171: - [ ] Test AgentRuntime CR has correct timeout values\n1172: - [ ] Verify timeouts are configurable in future\n1173: \n1174: **Verification**: Review AgentRuntime CR spec and verify timeouts\n1175: \n1176: ---\n1177: \n1178: ### Task 82: Test imagePullSecrets configuration\n1179: - [ ] Verify default imagePullSecrets is [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]\n1180: - [ ] Test AgentRuntime CR has imagePullSecrets\n1181: - [ ] Test Kubernetes Deployment has imagePullSecrets (if needed)\n1182: - [ ] Verify private images can be pulled\n1183: \n1184: **Verification**: Review resource specs and verify imagePullSecrets\n1185: \n1186: ---\n1187: \n1188: ### Task 83: Test env vars configuration\n1189: - [ ] Test WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL in env vars\n1190: - [ ] Test ROUTER_URL in env vars\n1191: - [ ] Test custom env vars in metadata\n1192: - [ [ ] Verify env vars are passed to container\n1193: - [ ] Verify env vars are in AgentRuntime CR\n1194: - [ ] Verify env vars are in Kubernetes Deployment\n1195: \n1196: **Verification**: Review resource specs and verify env vars\n1197: \n1198: ---\n1199: \n1200: ### Task 84: Test port configuration\n1201: - [ ] Test with default port (8080)\n1202: - [ ] Test with custom port from metadata\n1203: - [ ] Test with custom port from CLI\n1204: - [ ] Verify port is used in AgentRuntime CR\n1205: - [ ] Verify port is used in Kubernetes Deployment\n1206: - [ ] Verify port is used in Service\n1207: - [ ] Verify port is used in readiness probe\n1208: \n1209: **Verification**: Review resource specs and verify port configuration\n1210: \n1211: ---\n1212: \n1213: ### Task 85: Test entrypoint configuration\n1214: - [ ] Test with entrypoint from metadata\n1215: - [ ] Test with entrypoint override from CLI\n1216: - [ ] Verify entrypoint is used in AgentRuntime CR\n1217: - [ ] Verify entrypoint is used in Kubernetes Deployment\n1218: - [ ] Verify entrypoint format is correct\n1219: \n1220: **Verification**: Review resource specs and verify entrypoint\n1221: \n1222: ---\n1223: \n1224: ### Task 86: Test description field handling\n1225: - [ ] Test with description from metadata\n1226: - [ ] Test with description from CLI\n1227: - [ ] Test CLI override metadata\n1228: - [ ] Verify description is saved in metadata\n1229: - [ ] Verify description is used in future operations\n1230: \n1231: **Verification**: Test description handling and verify behavior\n1232: \n1233: ---\n1234: \n1235: ### Task 87: Test version field handling\n1236: - [ ] Test with version from metadata\n1237: - [ ] Test with version from CLI\n1238: - [ ] Test CLI override metadata\n1239: - [ ] Verify version is used in image URL\n1240: - [ ] Verify version is saved in metadata\n1241: \n1242: **Verification**: Test version handling and verify behavior\n1243: \n1244: ---\n1245: \n1246: ### Task 88: Test region field handling\n1247: - [ ] Test with region from metadata\n1248: - [ ] Test with region from CLI\n1249: - [ ] Test CLI override metadata\n1250: - [ ] Verify region is saved in metadata\n1251: - [ ] Verify region is used in cloud deployments (future)\n1252: \n1253: **Verification**: Test region handling and verify behavior\n1254: \n1255: ---\n1256: \n1257: ### Task 89: Final verification and cleanup\n1258: - [ ] Run full test suite: `pytest cmd/cli/ -v --cov`\n1259: - [ ] Verify all tests pass with >80% coverage\n1260: - [ ] Run `flake8 cmd/cli/` and fix any issues\n1261: - [ ] Run `mypy cmd/cli/` and fix any type errors\n1262: - [ ] Run `black --check cmd/cli/` and format if needed\n1263: - [ ] Review all code for TODO comments\n1264: - [ ] Review all code for FIXME comments\n1265: - [ ] Review all code for commented-out code\n1266: - [ ] Verify all exported functions have docstrings\n1267: - [ ] Verify all exported classes have docstrings\n1268: - [ ] Clean up any temporary test files\n1269: - [ ] Verify examples work correctly\n1270: - [ ] Verify README is up to date\n1271: - [ ] Verify help text is comprehensive\n1272: - [ ] Verify error messages are clear\n1273: \n1274: **Verification**: All verification steps pass with no errors or warnings\n1275: \n1276: ---\n1277: \n1278: ## Summary\n1279: \n1280: **Total Tasks**: 89\n1281: **Estimated Effort**: L (Large) - 40-50 hours\n1282: \n1283: ### Key Deliverables\n1284: 1. **Publish Command** - CLI command with comprehensive options\n1285: 2. **PublishRuntime** - Core publish orchestration logic\n1286: 3. **AgentCubeProvider** - Deployment using AgentRuntime CR\n1287: 4. **KubernetesProvider** - Deployment using Deployment/Service\n1288: 5. **DockerService Integration** - Image tagging and pushing\n1289: 6. **Metadata Updates** - Persist deployment information\n1290: 7. **Comprehensive Tests** - Unit, integration, and E2E tests\n1291: 8. **Documentation** - README, examples, and inline docs\n1292: \n1293: ### Success Criteria\n1294: - All Python files compile without errors\n1295: - All unit tests pass with >80% code coverage\n1296: - All integration tests pass\n1297: - All E2E tests pass\n1298: - `agentcube publish --help` displays comprehensive help\n1299: - Publish works with agentcube provider\n1300: - Publish works with k8s provider\n1301: - Local build mode works correctly\n1302: - Image push to registry works\n1303: - Registry authentication works\n1304: - AgentRuntime CR is created correctly\n1305: - Kubernetes Deployment/Service are created correctly\n1306: - Metadata is updated with deployment info\n1307: - Error handling is comprehensive with clear messages\n1308: - Verbose mode provides detailed logging\n1309: - Code passes static analysis (flake8, mypy, black)\n1310: - Documentation is complete and accurate\n1311: - Examples work correctly\n1312: \n1313: ### Dependencies\n1314: - Python 3.10+\n1315: - typer[all] >=0.9.0\n1316: - pydantic >=2.0.0\n1317: - pyyaml >=6.0\n1318: - docker >=6.0.0\n1319: - kubernetes >=28.0.0\n1320: - rich >=13.0.0\n1321: - pytest (for testing)\n1322: - flake8 (for linting)\n1323: - mypy (for type checking)\n1324: - black (for formatting)\n1325: - Docker (for local build mode)\n1326: - Kubernetes cluster (for testing)\n1327: \n1328: ### Blocked By\n1329: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n1330: \n1331: ### Blocks\n1332: - AR-023: CLI invoke command (depends on publish command)\n1333: - AR-024: CLI status command (depends on publish command)\n1334: \n1335: ### Notes\n1336: - Publish command depends on pack and build commands\n1337: - Supports both AgentCube and Kubernetes providers\n1338: - Local build mode requires Docker and registry access\n1339: - Cloud build mode is not yet implemented (raises NotImplementedError)\n1340: - Comprehensive error handling and logging\n1341: - Rich progress display for better UX\n1342: - Extensive test coverage ensures reliability\n1343: - Session management for agentcube provider\n1344: - Metadata persistence for deployment tracking\n\n(End of file - total 1344 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `cmd/cli`\n**Language**: Python\n**Size**: L\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify publish command interface in main.py\n- [ ] Verify publish command exists in agentcube/cli/main.py\n- [ ] Verify all required parameters are defined:\n  - [ ] workspace (default \".\", short flag \"-f\")\n  - [ ] version (optional)\n  - [ ] image_url (optional)\n  - [ ] image_username (optional)\n  - [ ] image_password (optional)\n  - [ ] description (optional)\n  - [ ] region (optional)\n  - [ ] cloud_provider (optional)","trunc